love you perfect and the billionaire boys club doubted that 
a television movie based on the earthquake could serve a purpose 
its too soon and too painful gross said i wouldnt want 
to intrude on anybodys tragedy as much as we love to sell 
shows and we like to do anything thats current i think wed be 
intruding on peoples pain 
such a program likely would include the story julio berumen the 
6yearold whose right leg was amputated above the knee when he was 
