an attorney who has handled more than 100 
toxic shock syndrome lawsuits says two lawyers for a tampon maker 
offered to pay him if he would stop taking such cases 
playtex family products inc signed a 500000 consulting 
agreement with another plaintiffs lawyer who has stopped pressing 
