to norways proposal to negotiate mutual notification of accidents 
involving ships including nuclearpowered submarines 
three soviet nuclearpowered submarines have been involved in 
accidents since april in the barents and norwegian seas 
in other comments gorbachev 
reversed decades of finlandization pressure on finland 
