of believers said glemp who wore a large silver cross around 
his neck 
i attach great hopes to this service today technology 
especially in the mass media helps us a lot and we would like to 
be able to pass on a richness of spirit 
the program is being produced by a newly formed religious 
programs desk within the episcopate the administrative arm of 
polands bishops 
state tv said the programs are produced on church premises and 
its only responsiblity is to broadcast the shows it receives from 
the episcopate 
the 20minute church programs are to be appear each thursday at 
625 pm on polish channel 1 in addition channel 2 will 
broadcast a 20minute evening prayer on tuesdays at 630 pm 
two months ago the church began broadcasting weekly radio 
programs 
this has been a year of major achievements for the church with 
the signing in may of a bill by parliament guaranteeing the right 
of the church to operate legally 
